data.description:
Utilities Included! Newly renovated 2nd Floor apartment/condo in Northwest DC. Centrally located near Catholic University, Children's, and numerous restaurants and attractions. Custom floors, bathroom, kitchen, and built-in shelving throughout. Upscale living at an affordable price. 

This one will not last long at this price! First Responders and Military Discounts.

No pets or smoking allowed.
